review_text:
Currently had been this amazing cozy cafe and bar which is located next to the  hub of hostel such as Flock ,Yog ,Wanderthirst and Aloobar 1000;
We have tried few items from menu  such as Chicken momo ,Grilled Pork chop and Chicken Kurkure which are very delicious and tasty at affordable  price.
Highly recommend to visit here cause of fusion meal ,Peaceful environment and Mini garden as well as highly experienced chef who  was used to  work aboard as chef
